#: index.docbook:158
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "A special 'trump' game is called the Grand. In this game no suit is trump "
#| "and only the four Jacks count as trump. This game type is indicated by "
#| "the symbol of a Jack's head [8] on the score board [6]."
