#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Strateegia ja nõuanded"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:184
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
#| "cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards "
#| "that are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of "
#| "those cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the "
#| "same suit, he can play with any other card including a 'trump' card."
msgid ""
"When the game starts, the starting player should play any of the face up "
"cards from own stack. If the second player currently has face up cards that "
"are of the same suit as the card played, he has to reply with one of those "
"cards. If, however, the second player does not have a card of the same suit, "
"he can play with any other card including a <quote>trump</quote> card."
msgstr ""
"Mängu alustades võib esimese käigu tegija käia suvalise kaardi oma "
"mängupakist, mis on näoga ülespoole. Kui teisel mängijal on oma näoga "
"ülespoole kaartide seas sama masti kaart, peab ta sellega vastama. Kui "
"teisel mängijal aga pole sama masti kaarti, võib ta käia suvalise kaardi oma "
"maitse kohaselt."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:189
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If there is at least one 'trump' card, the highest 'trump' wins both "
#| "cards."
msgid ""
"If there is at least one <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest "
"<quote>trump</quote> wins both cards."
msgstr "Kui on vähemalt üks trumpkaart, võidab tihi suurim trump."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:190
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If there is no 'trump' card, the highest card of the suit played by the "
#| "starting player wins both cards."
msgid ""
"If there is no <quote>trump</quote> card, the highest card of the suit "
"played by the starting player wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Kui trumpkaarti pole, võidab tihi selle masti kõrgeim kaart, mille käis "
"välja alustaja."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:191
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no 'trump' "
#| "card, he has to play any card and the starting player wins both cards."
msgid ""
"If the replying player has no card of the requested suit and no "
"<quote>trump</quote> card, he has to play any card and the starting player "
"wins both cards."
msgstr ""
"Kui vastasel pole samast mastist kaarti ega trumpi, peab ta käima mis tahes "
"kaardi ning alustaja võidab tihi."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:194
#, no-c-format
msgid "The player who wins the round leads the next one."
msgstr "Tihi võitnud mängija alustab järgmist käiku."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:199
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently asked questions"
msgstr "Korduma kippuvad küsimused"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:203
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I play with a different deck of cards?"
msgstr "Kas kaardipaki välimust saab ka vahetada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:204
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. Refer to <link linkend=\"deck_change\">this</link> section of "
"'Interface Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Jah, muidugi. Täpsemalt kõneleb sellest osa \"Liidese tutvustus\" vastav "
"<link linkend=\"deck_change\">sektsioon</link>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:207
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have made a mistake. Can I undo?"
msgstr "Tegin vea. Kas selle saab tagasi võtta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:208
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have an <quote>Undo</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ei, see mäng ei võimalda <quote>tagasivõtmist</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I use the keyboard to play this game?"
msgstr "Kas mängida saab ka klaviatuuri abil?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:212
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game cannot be played using keyboard."
msgstr "Ei, klaviatuuri abil seda mängida ei saa."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:215
#, no-c-format
msgid "I cannot figure out what to do here! Are there hints?"
msgstr "Ma ei saa aru, mida ma peaksin tegema! Kas mingeid vihjeid ei ole?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:216
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Hint</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ei, see mäng ei paku <quote>vihjeid</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:219
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"I have to quit the game now, but I am not finished yet. Can I save my "
"progress?"
msgstr ""
"Ma pean mängust väljuma, aga mäng ei ole veel läbi. Kas ma saan oma seisu "
"salvestada?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "No. This game does not have a <quote>Save State</quote> feature."
msgstr "Ei, see mäng ei võimalda <quote>seisu salvestamist</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I change players' names?"
msgstr "Kas mängijate nimesid saab muuta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:224
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes. To change the names displayed on the right hand side of the game screen "
"refer to <link linkend=\"name_change\">this</link> section of 'Interface "
"Overview' for details."
msgstr ""
"Jah. Sellest, kuidas muuta mänguaknas paremal näidatavaid nimesid, kõneleb "
"täpsemalt osa 'Liidese tutvustus' vastav <link linkend=\"name_change"
"\">sektsioon</link>."

